agents

Class CarSerializable

  • java.lang.Object
    • agents.CarSerializable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class CarSerializable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Serializable class to save the car information so that in a next time the car has some knowledge about the world. This information is the car knowledge about the world such as: the city structure, the unvisited roads that it came across its journey, the qualities values(QLearning) and the destination point for those values.
